result.name: Nam Kee Cafe

reviews.text: A HK style cafe with around 9 tables. Offer ome fast set (~$60) and home style dishes ($80~$150) both for bachelor or friend/family. I usually take away. Price is fair due to quiet corner location. Taste is ok for this price level and worth to try.
You don't feel full after having breakfast there, and they only dole out half a piece of toast. Do NOt come here for breakfast.
Good
